{"word":"τραφερός","slug":"τραφερός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n104601\" key=\"trafero/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τρᾰφερός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ά</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">τρέφω</etym>) <sense id=\"n104601.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">well-fed, fat,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἱ τραφεροί</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ τραφερά</foreign> the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fat ones,</tr_> i. e. fishes, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.44</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n104601.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> uses <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τραφερή</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γῆ</foreign>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Subst.\">Subst.</a></pos>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dry land,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐπὶ τραφερήν τε καὶ ὑγρήν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:308\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.308</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:98\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.98</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg002.perseus-grc1:43\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Cer.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">43</biblScope> </bibl>:—in later Poets as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νομὸς τ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0653.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1027\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arat.\">Arat.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1027</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κέλευθος ὑγρή τε τ. τε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:545\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.545</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τ. ἄρουρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:204\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ H.\">H.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.204</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἤθεα τ.</foreign> tracts <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">of dry land,</tr_> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:334\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.334</biblScope></bibl>. (In this sense it is from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρέφω</foreign> (A) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make thick.</tr_>)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}